result.name: AEON Lai Chi Kok Store

reviews.text:
A three storey department with all sorts of items for family. Baby/children toys, clothing, strollers, milk bottles. Adult clothing, sport clothes, office clothes, furnitures, beddings etc. 

And also the supermarket at ground floor has lots of fresh food like sushi, oysters, meats. The price is a bit of mark up but happy to pay the premium for the quality and variety

I love it. Pre-packaged meals, sushi and fruits/veggies on sale after 6pm or so.

Only downside that it's a pretty inconvenient detour for me which is why I don't go there often, maybe once in two weeks.
A nice supermarket full of Japanese stuff and food! 🌸
Very convenient for locals living in the area. But definitely not the best branch I've visited, strange layout and in need of a refurbishment. The best one is still the Taikoo branch.
a little convinient for those have small time in taking there groceries since some resto are inside the EON store

result.name: AEON荔枝角店

reviews.text: 附近只有呢個商場比較大啲🤗 有酒樓餐廳👌

這個百貨公司有超級市場,有買衣服的地方以及有買日常家居用品的地方,例如廚具,碗碟等等.
對於住在美孚和荔枝角的居民一定覺得十分方便(尤其是住在碧海藍天的居民一定覺得沒得輸）
裡面還有一些餐廳方便學生和居民用饍而且冷氣十足.
到此地方法：
第一,住美孚新村的居民可以考慮走過來.
第二,可以乘搭港鐵到荔枝角站,然後再行5至10分鐘就到.

其實一個地方能夠輕易地到達以及擁有很多不同類型的貨品給大家去購物真係值得一來.
電器部男售貨員主動詳盡，資訊我所需要(正選擇困難)歐洲/日式洗衣機各優越處解決問題並派說明書回家度尺寸選日式那型號

reviews.text:
跟日本非常相似，只是相似！
因為米的軟硬度，蔬菜的新鮮程度都不及日本，水壺沒有像日本的有冰塊，有點不對勁似的😅

要讚的是這分店的服務態度非常好！只是日文的歡迎語句需來點改進吧😂
咖哩飯🍛的咖哩可以選擇辣度，還有不同種類的小食。贊👍！

Came here almost closed, and they still take order. The taste of curry as good as in Japan also the portion really big. Don’t forget to order extra egg, because its so fluffy and melting in your mouth.

Great Japanese comfort curry, friendly staff, laid-back atmosphere hidden away at the back of a supermarket.
Pro tip: add cheese to your curry for extra gooey goodness!
很普通的味道，包裝即食的咖喱似乎更好味
